high_descs: Turn around to walk down the passage and turn left to enter the bedroom and reach the bed on the right.
Pick up the hammer from the bed.
Turn right and walk out the room and turn left to reach the kitchen on the right and face the cabinet on the left.
Put the hammer in the cabinet.
Look down at the countertop on the left of the coffee machine.
Pick up the hammer from the counter.
Look up to face the cabinet above the counter.
Put the hammer in the cabinet next to the other hammer.
anns.task_desc: Put two Hammer in the kitchen Cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and go through the door to the hallway, then take the first left into the bedroom, heading towards the bed.
Pick up the hammer from the bed.
Leave the room the way you came in, then turn left towards the shelves, then right into the cabinet area.
Place the hammer into the upper cabinet above the coffee machine.
Look down at the area to the left of the countertop.
Pick up the hammer on the counter.
Look up to the cabinet above the coffee machine where you put the first hammer.
Place the hammer down in the upper cabinet next to the first hammer.
anns.task_desc: Place two hammers into upper cabinets in a kitchen.

high_descs: Leave the room. At the next entrance, cross to the right and go to the bed. Turn right.
Take the hammer.
Leave the room. Turn left. When you reach the cabinet on the left, turn right and go to the coffee maker. Turn right to be in front of the coffee maker. Raise the hammer.
Open the cabinet doors. Place the hammer on the right side of the cabinet. Close the cabinet doors.
Move to the left of the countertop.
Take the hammer.
Move to be in front of the cabinet. Raise the hammer.
Open the cabinet. Place the hammer vertically on the left side of the cabinet. Close the cabinet doors.
anns.task_desc: Search for two hammers. Place the hammers inside the cabinet.
